    <refname>bg_run</refname>
    <refpurpose>Run a Scilab script at background</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Syntax</title>
   <synopsis>
   task = bg_run(fn)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
        <varlistentry>
            <term>fn :</term>
            <listitem><para> Scilab script name in string format</para></listitem>
        </varlistentry>
        <varlistentry>
            <term>task :</term>
            <listitem><para> Process ID for the task</para></listitem>
        </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
This is to sent the Scilab task to the background as silent process
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

